quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  43,61,"Wa-innahu laAAilmun lissaAAatifala tamtarunna biha wattabiAAooni hathasiratun mustaqeem"
  43,62,"Wala yasuddannakumu ashshaytanuinnahu lakum AAaduwwun mubeen"
  43,63,"Walamma jaa AAeesa bilbayyinatiqala qad ji/tukum bilhikmati wali-obayyinalakum baAAda allathee takhtalifoona feehi fattaqooAllaha waateeAAoon"
  43,64,"Inna Allaha huwa rabbee warabbukum faAAbudoohuhatha siratun mustaqeem"
  43,65,"Fakhtalafa al-ahzabumin baynihim fawaylun lillatheena thalamoomin AAathabi yawmin aleem"
  43,66,"Hal yanthuroona illa assaAAataan ta/tiyahum baghtatan wahum la yashAAuroon"
  43,67,"Al-akhillao yawma-ithin baAAduhumlibaAAdin AAaduwwun illa almuttaqeen"
  43,68,"Ya AAibadi la khawfunAAalaykumu alyawma wala antum tahzanoon"
  43,69,"Allatheena amanoo bi-ayatinawakanoo muslimeen"
  43,70,"Odkhuloo aljannata antum waazwajukumtuhbaroon"
  43,71,"Yutafu AAalayhim bisihafinmin thahabin waakwabin wafeeha matashtaheehi al-anfusu watalaththu al-aAAyunu waantum feehakhalidoon"
  43,72,"Watilka aljannatu allatee oorithtumoohabima kuntum taAAmaloon"
  43,73,"Lakum feeha fakihatunkatheeratun minha ta/kuloon"
